divs: Sighting DetailsI was just out side closing the back garage door and happened to be star watching, like I do a lot then I happened to see it. It was a white dot mixed with the stars but larger. Then turned blue and continued moving at a real slow speed from east to west. I have a couple still frams and about a minute of video recording. I have the ( Google ) star program and it was not a star on the chart.
